44 Sanidassanattika, Vitakkattika
Sanidassanattika, Vitakkattika
53.
168Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ nasavitakkasavicāraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anidassanaappaṭigho savitakkasavicāro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
169Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ naavitakkavicāramattaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca anidassanaappaṭigho avitakkavicāramatto dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā tīṇi…pe…  avigate tīṇi.
170Nasanidassanasappaṭighaṃ naavitakkaavicāraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca sanidassanasappaṭigho avitakkaavicāro dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā. (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā ekavīsa, ārammaṇe tīṇi…pe…  avigate ekavīsa.
